di depan hotel waktu itu?

125
00:07:10,282 --> 00:07:12,743
Kau mencoba membuat hotel jadi lelangan.

126
00:07:15,813 --> 00:07:17,022
Aku kehilangan nafsu makan, Hyung-nim.

127
00:07:17,652 --> 00:07:20,853
